snippet: Foreign Minister Yang Jiechi of China and his counterpart from Myanmar, U Wunna Maung Lwin, agreed to “properly settle matters” after Myanmar suspended construction of the Myitsone hydroelectric dam.
lead_paragraph: Foreign Minister Yang Jiechi of China and his counterpart from Myanmar, U Wunna Maung Lwin, agreed to “properly settle matters” after Myanmar suspended construction of the Myitsone hydroelectric dam.

headline.main: China and Myanmar to ‘Settle’ on Myitsone Dam
headline.print_headline: China and Myanmar to ‘Settle’ on Dam
